    id: 217,
    title: "“To My Love”",
    excerpt: "My Dearest, / Despite the miles and distance between us, my heart is always with you. / Your memories light up every morning,",
    full: `My Dearest,

Despite the miles and distance between us, my heart is always with you.
Your memories light up every morning,
And your love makes every night sweet.

You say you miss me so much,
And every moment your words play like music in my ears.
Every moment we’ve shared—walking, laughing, watching movies,
Shopping, and enjoying little meals together—
Becomes even more special with you by my side.

I know this distance is sometimes hard.
Even when you can’t comfort me,
Your words and your love are always with me.
“Always stay optimistic, my love,” you say,
And I live each day holding onto that hope.

Your love is as deep as the ocean,
As strong as rocks, as vast as the sky.
You said, “Until the seas run dry,
And the rocks crumble, I will be yours.”
Your loyalty, honesty, and devotion
Are the greatest treasures of my life.

Every day I think of you,
Your name echoes in every heartbeat.
And I believe that one day,
This distance will end, and we will be together forever.

You are my hope, my light in every dream.
And I am completely yours, just as you are mine.
Your love`,
